{
  "id": "adv_event_2411_01_05_02",
  "title": "最強の\nニコイチ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "聴いてくれてありがと～！　どうだった？？\n歌詞も振り付けも二人で一緒に作ったんだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for listening~! How was it??\nWe wrote the lyrics and choreography together~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.2085939408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9857583
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4000772873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "ご存じの通りこころ達はみなさんの投票によって\n生まれた、このフェスのための一日限定ユニットです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you know‚ we're formed by your votes‚\nand are a one-day-only unit for this festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4000772873,
      "endTime": 16.9671976486,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13866.652424999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.1667439539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今日優勝出来なかったらkana達は解散……\nもう二度とこの曲を披露することはないかもなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ if we don't win today‚ kana's unit will disband…\nWe may never perform this song again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1667439539,
      "endTime": 27.758353718000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（解散……？　二度と披露しない……？）\n（いやいやいや、俺は一言もそんなこと言ってないぞ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Disband…? Never perform again…?）\n（No‚ no‚ no‚ I never said a word like that!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9667439539,
      "endTime": 35.9101307948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0870590245
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1000854253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、短い間だったけど本当にありがと\n凄く楽しかった……もっとこころちゃんと……ぐすっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro-chan‚ it was a short time‚ but thank you so much\nIt was so much fun… More with Kokoro-chan… sniff",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1000854253,
      "endTime": 47.759155249500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7334157068
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.966752092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "kanaちゃん、泣かないで。まだ結果は出てないよ\nkanaちゃんが泣いたらこころまで……うわぁん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-chan‚ don't cry. The results aren't out yet\nIf kana-chan cries‚ Kokoro-chan will cry too… waaaah",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.966752092,
      "endTime": 59.6600626389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.866752092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうだよね……ぐすんっ……ごめん\nkana、普段はあんまり泣いたりしないんだけどなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ right… sniff… I'm sorry\nkana‚ don't usually cry that much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.866752092,
      "endTime": 70.0062315384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan023.m4a",
      "text": "このユニットはこころちゃんとファンのみんなと一緒に\n作り上げた大切なものだからなんか思い入れが強くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This unit is something important that\nI created together with Kokoro-chan and all the fans‚ so I have a lot of attachment to it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2000854253,
      "endTime": 79.6814685583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.866752092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日のために出来ることは全部やってきたから\nどんな結果になっても悔いはないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we've done everything we could for today‚\nso no matter what the outcome‚ I have no regrets",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.866752092,
      "endTime": 86.80704664379999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0000854253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "こころも同じ気持ちだよ。どんな結果になっても……\nこれからも仲良くしてね！　kanaちゃん大好き",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro feels the same way. No matter what the outcome…\nLet's continue to be besties! I love you‚ kana-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0000854253,
      "endTime": 96.7706292867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.0334157068
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.966752092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みなさん！　kana（こころ）達に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! Please cast your final vote",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.966752092,
      "endTime": 99.3334157068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最終投票、よろしくお願いします……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for kana(Kokoro)…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3334157068,
      "endTime": 102.68480190439999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.8500854253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よっしゃぁぁぁ！！　優勝じゃ～～～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yessssss!! I'm a winner~~~~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9000854253,
      "endTime": 108.5753009557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.300084408
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.766752092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "冠番組、冠番組、嬉しいな～！\nこころがリズノワ初の冠番組を持てるなんて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Flagship show‚ Flagship show‚ so happy~!\nKokoro can do the first Flagship show in LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.766752092,
      "endTime": 116.599337236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8000854253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan027.m4a",
      "text": "ニコニコアイスの全国CM……これできっと……\nお父さんはkanaを見つけてくれる。気付いてくれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A nationwide Nico Nico Ice CM… I'm sure this will…\nDad will find kana. He must notice me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8000854253,
      "endTime": 125.7430555105,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.333333300001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.9334187586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも！　投票前最後の嘘MCは一体なんなんですか\n解散とか二度と披露しないとか、どういうことです！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you! What the hell was that last lie in the MC before the vote\nWhat do you mean‚ disbanding or never performing again!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9334187586,
      "endTime": 133.4766388018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.6667663335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan028.m4a",
      "text": "うっさいな～。別に嘘はついてないでしょ\n「披露することはない『かも』」としか言ってないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's noisy~. I wasn't really lying\nI only said 'Maybe' we'll never perform again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6667663335,
      "endTime": 141.23660752770002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.4334330002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ、kanaさんは悪くありません！\nみなさんの投票で決まったんですから優勝は優勝です～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ kana-san is not bad!\nIt was decided by everyone's votes‚ so the winner is the winner~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4334330002,
      "endTime": 150.2401907364,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13899.963378799981
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.4334330002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうですけど……ファンの人達を騙すみたいな\n演出は……ちょっとどこ行くんですか！　話はまだ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true… but this production that seems to be\ndeceiving the fans… wait‚ where are you going! I'm not finished yet――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4334330002,
      "endTime": 158.8880819718,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.691080699997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.0001240809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan030.m4a",
      "text": "優勝インタビューに決まってるじゃん\nじゃーねーー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's already been decided that we'll have a winning interview\nThenー See youーー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.0001240809,
      "endTime": 162.6367906649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.8334574143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
